setting up GitHub and Heroku account
1) Install additional heroku account (my personal) 
  download a heroku plugin::
   heroku plugins:install git://github.com/ddollar/heroku-accounts.git
  
  
user: gikchumak@bellsouth.net
password: Karman2015

> heroku status
> heroku logout
> heroku login


Create personal Github account: 
git config --global user.name "ichumanov"
git config --global user.email "gikchumak@bellsouth.net"

Creating an empty local repository for your personal projects (This will create .git directory)
